-- B y   K i m   M c L a u g h l i n
-- 2010-10-04T09:33:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/robert-edwards-u-k-test-tube-baby-pioneer-wins-nobel-prize-for-medicine.html
Robert Edwards, a British
physiologist and a pioneer in reproductive medicine, won the
2010 Nobel prize in Physiology or Medicine, the Nobel Assembly
at Karolinska Institutet said today in a statement in Stockholm.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
